She looked at Black Aracnia.  She stood there trying to look big and 
tough, knowing it wouldn't do much goos anyway, but she had to try.
"I would like to join your group.  I've had it up to here with 
Megatron." as she raised her hand up to an inch over her head.
"I get to risk my life and or what? Nothing. I'm tired of working for 
loosers. I want to be on the winning team. Your's." she said with a 
smile.
